data.description: This charming turn-key modern Shawnee home sits on .89 acres of mature trees and no backyard neighbors. Conveniently located close to I-75 in a semi-rural neighborhood. This bright & cheery well-kept beauty will be a great starter home or for a small family to grow in. Just unpack your boxes and start enjoying this wonderful ranch home. This home features a large living room, a dedicated dining space and a breakfast nook, and a 10x24 one car garage that has plenty of storage. Updated bathrooms and kitchen with solid surface counters. Each room is Freshly painted in neutral color scheme. Garden shed is included! Don't miss your chance to see this amazing property.
